response.original_title: The Chronicles of Narnia: The Voyage of the Dawn Treader
response.overview: This time around Edmund and Lucy Pevensie, along with their pesky cousin Eustace Scrubb find themselves swallowed into a painting and on to a fantastic Narnian ship headed for the very edges of the world.
response.tagline: Return to magic. Return to hope. Return to Narnia.
